# JEPA

A JEPA (Joint Embedding Predictive Architecture) training framework to train JEPAs.

## Features
- Modular model, data, trainer structure
- Easy to extend with new encoders/predictors
- CLI-based training and evaluation

## Getting Started
```bash
pip install -e .
jepa-train
```
